originalText.text: We often rent a bus to take the kids from school on field trips. Over the years, I've found that Corporate & Group Bus Rental has the best service. It doesn't matter if we need one bus or several. The driver is always very professional and safe, and the bus is always clean and smells nice. I was told that each driver's safety record and background are checked, so parents feel even more comfortable with them. I would not want the child to be in any danger and Corporate & Group Bus Rental is the company to trust!
